png

Class PngDirectory

  • java.lang.Object
    • png.PngDirectory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Directory<PngChunk>, java.lang.Iterable<PngChunk>

    public class PngDirectory
extends java.lang.Object
implements Directory<PngChunk>
    Manages a collection of PngChunk objects that all belong to a specific ChunkType.Category.

    This class implements the Directory interface, providing methods for adding, retrieving, and iterating over the PngChunk objects. It enforces that all chunks added to the directory must match the directory's predefined ChunkType.Category.
